### Crear precio
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/prices
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "profileId": "{{profileId}}",
  "unitPrice": 250.00,
  "notes": "Precio contado"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("priceId", response.body.id);
%}

### Listar precios
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/prices?page=0&size=20
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Eliminar precio
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/prices/{{priceId}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Crear factura DRAFT
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices?customerName=Cliente%20Ejemplo&customerVat=B12345678
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

> {%
    client.global.set("invoiceId", response.body.id);
%}

### Agregar línea 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/lines
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lineNumber": 1,
  "description": "Viga HEB200 — 6 metros",
  "profileId": "{{profileId}}",
  "quantity": 6.00,
  "unitPrice": 250.00
}

> {%
    client.global.set("lineId", response.body.id);
%}

### Agregar línea 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/lines
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lineNumber": 2,
  "description": "Mano de obra — corte y soldadura",
  "quantity": 4.00,
  "unitPrice": 75.00
}

### Ver líneas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/lines
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Ver factura
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices/{{invoiceId}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Emitir factura
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/issue
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Pagar factura
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/pay
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Crear factura para cancelar
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices?customerName=Test
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

> {%
    client.global.set("cancelInvoiceId", response.body.id);
%}

### Cancelar factura
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices/{{cancelInvoiceId}}/cancel
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Listar facturas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices?page=0&size=20
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
